American.

11:08.736 --> 11:13.112
- Name?
- Jesus... William Hayes.

11:13.281 --> 11:19.996
- Name?
- Hayes. H-A-Y-E-S.

13:00.939 --> 13:06.100
Howdy, Billy.
How are you doing? Okay?

13:08.488 --> 13:14.942
I think these gentlemen
have finished for the time being.

13:15.120 --> 13:19.035
If you'd like
to put your clothes on.

13:40.522 --> 13:44.984
The officer wants to know
if you're afraid.

13:45.153 --> 13:48.403
No, I'm not afraid.

14:02.672 --> 14:06.586
The officer said
there's nothing to be afraid of.

14:06.759 --> 14:10.674
Co-operate,
and you'll be on the plane home.

14:20.148 --> 14:25.309
- Where did you get the hashish?
- From a cab driver.

14:25.488 --> 14:28.489
In the playing shop at the bazaar.

14:41.421 --> 14:47.424
- Would you recognise him again?
- I think so.

14:54.603 --> 14:57.723
You decided to fly at a bad time.

14:57.898 --> 15:03.521
Guerrillas all over the place,
blowing up planes...

15:03.696 --> 15:08.488
Four planes in four days.
Don't you read the newspapers?

15:08.659 --> 15:12.822
There's been a shit storm
over the flow of heroin from Turkey.

15:12.997 --> 15:16.864
- I didn't have heroin.
- A drug is a drug.

15:17.043 --> 15:21.670
It was my first time.
It was only two kilos.

15:21.840 --> 15:25.374
It doesn't matter
if it was 2 or 200 kilos.

15:25.552 --> 15:29.846
Catching you shows the world
Turkey is fighting the drug trade.

15:30.015 --> 15:35.602
- Are you with the Consulate?
- Something like that. Cigarette?

