16:06.971 --> 16:13.889
- She didn't know anything about it.
- Lucky girl.

16:14.063 --> 16:18.773
- She used to say I was lucky.
- Les hope so, Billy.

20:30.129 --> 20:33.047
You seem like a nice enough kid.

20:33.216 --> 20:38.293
But you try it,
and I'll blow your brains out.

21:07.335 --> 21:14.169
Mom and Dad, this is the hardest
letter I've ever had to write.

21:14.343 --> 21:20.845
I hoped to get out of this quickly,
so you'd never know about it.

21:21.017 --> 21:27.386
But that just isn't possible now.
I don't know whas going to happen.

21:27.565 --> 21:31.943
What can I say to you?
