21:32.112 --> 21:37.107
Will it ease the pain,
the shame you must be feeling?

21:37.284 --> 21:40.699
Forgive me, please.

21:55.970 --> 21:59.220
Could I have a blanket?

21:59.390 --> 22:02.890
Is cold.
Could I have a blanket?

22:03.061 --> 22:09.314
- A blanket!
- Too late. Tomorrow.

22:09.485 --> 22:16.734
He'll be here tomorrow, I think.
Goodnight.

22:51.696 --> 22:55.944
- Can you speak English?
- Your cell is open.

22:56.118 --> 23:00.495
Blankets, three cells down.
You get me one.

24:18.665 --> 24:21.203
I needed a blanket.

24:24.213 --> 24:27.214
William Hayes.

24:42.524 --> 24:45.692
I needed a blanket, I was cold!

26:01.150 --> 26:03.558
Jesus...

26:03.736 --> 26:06.986
Come on, you must stand.

26:08.031 --> 26:11.946
You'd better walk around,
or your feet will swell up.

26:12.119 --> 26:19.287
- You've got to be crazy.
- We all are. Smoke some of this.

26:20.171 --> 26:26.755
You've been out for days,
talking all kinds of shit.

26:26.928 --> 26:30.463
- How does it feel?
- About as good as it looks.

26:30.640 --> 26:38.055
Gecmis olsun. Is Turkish.
It means, "May it pass quickly."

26:39.566 --> 26:43.695
- It looks like a cheap hotel.
- The room service is lousy.

26:43.863 --> 26:48.156
I'm Jimmy Booth.
This is Erich... something Swedish.

26:48.325 --> 26:51.410
- Just Erich.
- He cleaned you up.

26:51.579 --> 26:56.158
Thanks. I'm Billy Hayes...
at least I used to be.

27:34.625 --> 27:38.789
- Why peacocks?
- They use them instead of dogs.

27:38.963 --> 27:45.630
They scream like mad if they're
disturbed and they don't get rabies.

27:46.721 --> 27:52.013
- Who are the kids?
- Little fuckers...

27:52.186 --> 27:56.765
Thieves, rapists, murderers...
You name it, they do it.

27:56.941 --> 28:01.021
Don't trust any of them.
They tell Rifki everything.

28:01.195 --> 28:04.481
He's the squeal around here.
He sells tea, -

28:04.657 --> 28:08.441
- hash, blankets,
anything for a buck.

28:09.995 --> 28:13.697
- What are you in for, hash?
- Yeah.

28:15.251 --> 28:18.170
- Where?
- At the airport.

28:18.339 --> 28:24.508
Thas heavy.
This ain't the good old USA.

28:24.679 --> 28:28.463
In Turkey, is a fucking accident
