29:39.176 --> 29:44.596
- What about you?
- Hashish, like most foreigners.

29:44.764 --> 29:49.474
- What did they give you?
- 12 years. I had 100 grams.

29:49.645 --> 29:55.897
You've got to get a good lawyer.
Talk to the Englishman. Max.

29:56.068 --> 29:59.936
He's been in the longest.
Seven years.

30:17.383 --> 30:21.677
Gastro. Stomach medicine.

30:23.473 --> 30:28.551
Is got codeine in it.
Is the best I can do around here.

30:28.729 --> 30:31.101
Max...

30:31.273 --> 30:35.485
- Lawyers?
- Oh, yeah.

30:36.653 --> 30:40.734
There's no straight lawyers
in Turkey.

30:40.908 --> 30:44.527
They're all bent.

30:44.704 --> 30:49.995
Bent as hairpins.
Occupational necessity.

30:50.168 --> 30:54.961
They have special classes
in corruption at night school.

30:56.342 --> 31:00.174
If you're suspected of honesty,
you're disbarred.

31:05.308 --> 31:09.853
I knew a lawyer fellow once.

31:10.023 --> 31:14.686
He got that Frenchman off.
La Roche.

31:18.031 --> 31:21.151
A big smuggler.

31:21.326 --> 31:24.660
200 kilos.

31:26.082 --> 31:30.791
He put enough bread
in enough pockets. Got bail.

31:30.962 --> 31:34.580
Vanished.

31:34.758 --> 31:39.634
- His name?
- Who?

31:39.805 --> 31:45.226
- The lawyer.
- Lawyer?

31:45.393 --> 31:50.103
Who got the Frenchman off.

31:51.984 --> 31:57.821
Yesil is his name.

31:59.701 --> 32:03.699
I don't know anything else
about him.

32:03.872 --> 32:07.289
Yesil.

32:09.170 --> 32:14.164
The best thing to do
is get your ass out of here.

32:14.341 --> 32:18.754
- Yeah, but how?
- Catch the midnight express.

32:18.930 --> 32:22.097
Whas that?

32:24.727 --> 32:33.817
Is not a train.
Is a prison word for... escape.

32:38.492 --> 32:41.577
