33:28.588 --> 33:31.506
Dad, I'm sorry.

33:31.675 --> 33:34.878
Forget it.

33:35.053 --> 33:41.852
I'll punch you in the nose later.
We've got to get you out of here.

33:42.020 --> 33:46.728
This is a suit I brought for you.

33:47.984 --> 33:51.519
Smarten you up a little.

33:54.575 --> 33:58.785
- Are you all right?
- Yeah.

33:58.953 --> 34:02.323
How's Mom?

34:02.499 --> 34:06.498
Well, she's bad.

34:06.671 --> 34:11.498
She couldn't make the trip.
You know Mom. Her boy...

34:14.344 --> 34:18.045
Susan told us
before we got your letter.

34:18.225 --> 34:21.428
She's saving to come back here...

34:21.603 --> 34:27.273
Don't let her come.
How's Rob? How's Peg?

34:27.443 --> 34:30.728
They're the same. You know.

34:30.904 --> 34:36.112
We told the neighbours
you were in hospital in Europe.

34:36.286 --> 34:42.788
This is Stanley Daniels.
He's the American Consul here.

34:42.958 --> 34:50.754
Billy, we're going to do everything
in our power to get you out of here.

34:50.926 --> 34:57.843
