35:02.356 --> 35:06.567
We'll get the right court
and the right judge.

35:06.735 --> 35:10.187
I'll arrange everything, just right.

35:11.615 --> 35:18.032
I understand that if you get bail,
is easy to get across the border.

35:18.205 --> 35:24.575
Thas what we're shooting for.
