37:02.777 --> 37:07.687
Let me work with Mr. Daniels
and Mr. Yesil here.

37:07.865 --> 37:11.115
We'll get you out, okay?

37:11.285 --> 37:15.235
Hey, Billy... Okay?

37:18.000 --> 37:20.456
Okay.

