it works out to about three years.

40:56.652 --> 40:59.819
And then there's the appeal.

40:59.989 --> 41:08.412
Daniels and Yesil
are all working for you.

41:08.581 --> 41:12.365
We're trying to get you transferred.

41:12.543 --> 41:18.416
