a political amnesty any month now.

41:22.054 --> 41:25.969
All right, Billy...

41:26.142 --> 41:31.812
I know it sounds tough,
but we are going to get you out.

41:31.980 --> 41:37.320
I promise you.
Don't do anything stupid.

41:37.486 --> 41:41.188
They could play with your sentence.

41:42.993 --> 41:46.197
All right, now...

41:48.750 --> 41:55.168
I'm putting $500 in the bank.
Anything you need, you write.

41:55.340 --> 42:00.547
There's food here,
candy, writing paper, -

42:00.720 --> 42:08.052
