42:20.533 --> 42:25.076
Jesus!

42:28.917 --> 42:36.000
If I could be where you are...
I'd be there.

42:38.760 --> 42:42.379
I love you, Dad.

43:12.130 --> 43:16.627
You take good care of my boy,
