We have to be in here together.

49:32.956 --> 49:36.786
For all the money you've got,
you've got nothing.

49:36.959 --> 49:41.835
- You are American, you don't know.
- Know what?

49:42.006 --> 49:44.165
Dog eat dog.

49:44.342 --> 49:48.589
You fuck other man before he
fucks you. And you must fuck last.

49:57.023 --> 50:00.973
Come on down.

50:06.742 --> 50:13.575
Egbert...
Sodding cat.

52:43.826 --> 52:46.115
William!

52:46.287 --> 52:50.700
Are you all right?

52:50.876 --> 52:55.537
