57:00.851 --> 57:04.138
All we have to do...

57:04.314 --> 57:09.474
We only have to use your screwdriver
to scrape the mortar out.

57:09.652 --> 57:13.567
We pull out three stones
and squeeze through...

57:22.917 --> 57:27.414
Squeeze through,
and get our ass down the shaft.

57:27.589 --> 57:32.299
- Is a two-night operation.
